[SN]TITLE[SN]
Inquiry launched after Wrexham man's tractor death

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An investigation has been launched into the death of 68-year-old man who became trapped under a tractor and trailer, police have said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened in a field at Llanfynydd, Wrexham, on Monday evening.
North Wales Police said the man was pronounced dead at the scene and the coroner has been informed.
The Health and Safety Executive is investigating.
